race.comment: STAR FURY (6) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (23.29) at Warragul. Must come into calculations. KRAMER'S KING (7) is progressing well scoring last time out (22.68) at Geelong and bringing up his 12th career win. Form at this distance is sound. Boasts two wins from four starts out of this box. Bold showing expected again. TRICKY DISCO (8) hit the frame last time at this track but just a few starts ago ran blistering time when scoring over 400m at Geelong in 22.52. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time.
